Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.150
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:06.150 --> 00:00:07.600
JESSE HAINES: Welcome to Google.

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:09.812
SARAH KESSLER: Thank you
