a split structure, one

00:34:16.929 --> 00:34:18.694
for the services--

00:34:18.694 --> 00:34:20.110
[INAUDIBLE] and
all those things--

00:34:20.110 --> 00:34:24.070
and another one which is
going to be the archaic legacy

00:34:24.070 --> 00:34:28.870
level things,
exploiting workers?

00:34:28.870 --> 00:34:32.230
SARAH KESSLER: This is
an interesting question.

00:34:32.230 --> 00:34:39.580
Because if you look at
