00:34:46.690 --> 00:34:51.290
or on contract, than they
do employed in Cupertino.

00:34:51.290 --> 00:34:54.190
So this fragmentation
of work has already

00:34:54.190 --> 00:34:59.580
happened in the goods
side of things, in a way.

00:34:59.580 --> 00:35:02.890
You also have temp workers
