00:35:02.890 --> 00:35:05.350
There are some things
about factories which--

00:35:05.350 --> 00:35:08.890
safety things, which
make this a difficult--

00:35:08.890 --> 00:35:13.860
having a new workforce every
day is just not practical

00:35:13.860 --> 00:35:18.130
But I don't know what the
split is, in terms of it

00:35:18.130 --> 00:35:21.610
being a totally different
economy for services.

00:35:21.610 --> 00:35:22.450
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

00:35:22.450 --> 00:35:23.590
SARAH KESSLER: Sorry I
don't have a better answer.

00:35:23.590 --> 00:35:24.720
AUDIENCE: No, you
[INAUDIBLE] the question.

